Kakariko Village from The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time
This is my 10th? map - the first one I've released however. I payed very close attention to detail (hence the fog to improve performance-which is great btw).
This map is a tribute to (in my opinion) the greatest role-playing/adventure game ever made -- created for (fact) the greatest multiplayer first-person shooter ever made. 
46 spawn points total
